name alphalph
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Convert numbers to letters
longdesc Provides commands \alphalph and \AlphAlph. They are like
longdesc \number but the expansion consists of lowercase and uppercase
longdesc letters respectively (1 to a, 26 to z, 27 to aa, 52 to zz, 53
longdesc to ba, 702 to zz, 703 to aaa, etc.). Can be used as a
longdesc replacement for LaTeX's \@alph and \@Alph macros.
