name arphic
category Package
revision 15878
shortdesc Arphic (Chinese) font packages
longdesc These are font bundles for the Chinese Arphic fonts which work
longdesc with the CJK package. TrueType versions of these fonts for use
longdesc with XeLaTeX and LuaLaTeX are provided by the arphic-ttf
longdesc package. Arphic is actually the name of the company which
longdesc created these fonts (and put them under a GPL-like licence).
