name etexcmds
category Package
revision 78101
shortdesc Avoid name clashes with e-TeX commands
longdesc New primitive commands are introduced in e-TeX; sometimes the
longdesc names collide with existing macros. This package solves the
longdesc name clashes by adding a prefix to e-TeX's commands. For
longdesc example, eTeX's \unexpanded is provided as \etex@unexpanded.
