name feynmp-auto
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Automatic processing of feynmp graphics
longdesc The package takes care of running Metapost on the output files
longdesc produced by the feynmp package, so that the compiled pictures
longdesc will be available in the next run of LaTeX. The package honours
longdesc options that apply to feynmp.
