name fontwrap
category Package
revision 15878
shortdesc Bind fonts to specific unicode blocks
longdesc The package (which runs under XeLaTeX) lets you bind fonts to
longdesc specific unicode blocks, for automatic font tagging of
longdesc multilingual text. The package uses Perl (via perltex) to
longdesc construct its tables.
