name latex-lab
category Package
revision 76739
shortdesc LaTeX laboratory
longdesc This bundle holds optional files that are loaded in certain
longdesc situations by kernel code (if available). While this code is
longdesc still in development and the use is experimental, it is stored
longdesc outside the format so that there can be intermediate releases
longdesc not affecting the production use of LaTeX. Once the code is
longdesc finalized and properly tested it will eventually move to the
longdesc kernel and the corresponding file in this bundle will vanish.
longdesc Note that none of these files are directly user accessible in
longdesc documents (i.e., they aren't packages), so the process is
longdesc transparent to documents already using the new functionality.
containersize 56400
containerchecksum b16fc432bc8c7c15cb3ca21b73bea3592a5fa4a099e124264412ca9ca6a2b31d9d2781d9c02b21b3d0386c2429d764680942e26e6422d1819a948a71a3939712
