name mfware
category TLCore
revision 77830
shortdesc Supporting tools for Metafont: gftodvi, gftopk, gftype, mft
longdesc A collection of programs (as web source) for processing the
longdesc output of Metafont. They include: gftodvi (for making proof
longdesc sheets of letters); gftopk (translate gf bitmap files to pk
longdesc bitmaps); gftype (human-readable dump of gf files); mft
longdesc (prettyprint Metafont source).
depend mfware.ARCH
