name mpcolornames
category Package
revision 23252
shortdesc Extend list of predefined colour names for MetaPost
longdesc The MetaPost format plain.mp provides only five built-in colour
longdesc names (variables), all of which are defined in the RGB model:
longdesc red, green and blue for the primary colours and black and
longdesc white. The package makes more than 500 colour names from
longdesc different colour sets in different colour models available to
longdesc MetaPost. Colour sets include X11, SVG, DVIPS and xcolor
longdesc specifications.
