name pdfmanagement
category Package
revision 79047
shortdesc LaTeX PDF management bundle
longdesc This package is used to load LaTeX's PDF management code. The
longdesc PDF management code offers backend independent interfaces to
longdesc central PDF dictionaries, tools to create annotations,
longdesc outlines, form Xobjects, form fields, to embed files, and to
longdesc handle PDF standards. The code is currently provided as
longdesc independent package. It is automatically loaded if a document
longdesc uses \DocumentMetadata. It can also be loaded as a package. At
longdesc a later stage it will be integrated into the LaTeX kernel (or
longdesc in parts into permanent support packages).
